name: Jolly Origins
description:
Bonus Content

(Director’s Cut) I consumed half of the 16 oz glass of vodka mixed with gummy bears and sugar powder within 2 minutes. The drink was so savoring and smooth easy to mistake it for juice, and I underestimated the strength of the vodka. It wasn't long before I transcended to Jolly Paradise. The vodka-doused blue gummy bears waited patiently at the top to further my intoxication state. This visual is what I saw after every minute that passed.

* Interacting with this object will be like interacting with a drunk person. It has a mind of its own. *

‘Jolly Paradise Collection.' 

Rarity: Diamond rare

Collectors who own this interactive NFT successfully collected 3/3 of the ‘Jolly Paradise Collection’ Congratulations and enjoy an augmented or virtual reality experience. Owners of this NFT own the commercial license to download and reuse the 3D file.
